These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, iris
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, grapefruit
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, water
1. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person who growsiris is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Flower   | iris    | lily |
| Food         | grapefruit | nectarine    |
| Beverage     | lemonade     | water      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, pall-mall
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, aconite
City: hamburg, boston
1. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Cigar      | pall-mall  | bluemaster   |
| Flower   | aconite | marigold  |
| City     | boston   | hamburg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
City: hamburg, prague
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, bolivar
There are 2 different favourite colors: purple, light-blue
1. the person traveling to prague is in an even position##4
2. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| City         | hamburg   | prague  |
| Cigar   | bolivar | swisher  |
| Color         | purple   | light-blue |

