.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, reading
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, grey
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, basketball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Hobby          | baking | reading |
| Color   | grey   | mauve   |
| Sport     | basketball       | volleyball      |

