House: colonial, palace
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, indian
1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the palace house##1
2. the dutch is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |
| Game        | scrabble      | canasta  |
| House       | palace     | colonial    |
| Nationality   | dutch | indian |

