.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, orchid
There are 2 different nationalities: mexican, indian
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, country
1. the fan of country is on the left of the mexican##1
2. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
3. the person who growslily is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Flower    | orchid | lily     |
| Nationality     | indian | mexican |
| Music-Genre   | country | blues    |

