The people prefer 2 different music-genres: country, soul
1. the fan of soul is on the right of the project-manager##1
2. the owner of the mouse is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |
| Pet   | pony | mouse     |
| Job       | project-manager        | software-developer    |
| Music-Genre      | country  | soul |

