.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-11::.
2 different pets are kept: goat, hedgehog
There are 2 different favourite colors: aquamarine, white
City: paris, san-francisco
1. the person who likes white is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
2. the person who likes white is in an odd position##4
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Pet           | hedgehog     | goat |
| Color   | white | aquamarine  |
| City     | san-francisco      | paris |

