.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-20::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, may
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, daffodil
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, goat
1. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Birthday   | september | may |
| Flower   | azalea  | daffodil  |
| Pet     | goat | rabbit    |

 